Package: IrregLong
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of Longitudinal Data with Irregular Observation Times
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-01-16
Author: Eleanor Pullenayegum
Maintainer: Eleanor Pullenayegum <eleanor.pullenayegum@sickkids.ca>
Description: Analysis of longitudinal data for which the times of observation are random variables that are potentially associated with the outcome process. The package includes inverse-intensity weighting and multiple outputation methods.
Depends:
    survival, geepack, frailtypack, R (>= 2.10)
License: GPL-3
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    nlme,
    MEMSS,
    geesmv
VignetteBuilder: knitr
LazyData: true
